title: Geert Wilders almost drowned out by protesters at Perth media conference for Australian Liberty Alliance
text: A small but vocal group of protesters almost drown out controversial Dutch politician Geert Wilders at a media conference in Perth to announce Senate candidates for the new Australian Liberty Alliance. ...
